messages.message: @mfichman can you force merge now? https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/62993 CI is marked as failed but based on the logs im pretty sure it ran everything it needed to and then timed out right before going to the next stage https://jenkins.instabase.com/blue/organizations/jenkins/instabase/detail/PR-62993/35/pipeline#step-43-log-354

The tests have been so flakey for me

It helps, b/c then the diff is smaller, and fewer tests run.
